The following index definition named `default` indexes the `title`
field in the `movies`  collection as MongoDB Search `token` type:

```javascript
{
  "mappings": {
    "dynamic": false,
    "fields": {
      "title": {
        "type": "token",
        "normalizer": "lowercase"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

The following query searches for movie titles that contain characters
between `city` and `country`. It includes a [$limit](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/limit) stage
to limit the output to 5 results and a [$project](manual/reference/operator/aggregation/project) stage to
exclude all fields except `title`.

**Input:**

```json
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "range": {
        "path": "title",
        "gt": "city",
        "lt": "country"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$limit": 5
  },
  {
    "$project": {
      "_id": 0,
      "title": 1
    }
  }
])
```

**Output:**

```json
[
  { title: 'Civilization' },
  { title: 'Clash of the Wolves' },
  { title: 'City Lights' },
  { title: 'Comradeship' },
  { title: 'Come and Get It' }
]
```

The following query searches the `funding_rounds.raised_amount` field in
the `sample_training.companies` collection for amount greater than or
equal to `500000` and less than or equal to `1000000`. It uses the
`returnStoredSource: true` and `returnScope` to retrieve and return
the fields within the `funding_rounds` array of objects, which are
stored on `mongot`. The query uses the sample index from the [embeddedDocuments](bson-data-types-embedded-documents)
example.

âž¤ Try this in the [Search Playground](https://search-playground.mongodb.com/tools/code-sandbox/snapshots/68fbe4132ca0a88c52924bbb).
The results in the MongoDB Search Playground might vary because the data in the
MongoDB Search Playground is smaller than the sample collection used in the
following example.

**Input:**

```json
db.companies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "range": {
        "path": "funding_rounds.raised_amount",
        "gte": 500000,
        "lte": 1000000
      },
      "returnStoredSource": true,
      "returnScope": {
        "path": "funding_rounds"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$limit": 5
  }
])
```

**Output:**

```json
[
  {
    round_code: 'angel',
    raised_amount: 500000,
    raised_currency_code: 'USD'
  },
  {
    round_code: 'angel',
    raised_amount: 800000,
    raised_currency_code: 'USD'
  },
